Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:09.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:20.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:39.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:46.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:54.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:59.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:07.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:14.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:21.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:28.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:54.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, the elder is summoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:04.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aira and Hanna are going\Nto give it a try today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, here she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aira, Hanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure you want to do this?\NOf course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:43.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know how long we've been\Npracticing towards this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad they chose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:50.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's always been my dream to\Nbe like you and Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and to do the Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:57.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra and Sibylla Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:03.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was they who bestowed us\Nwith the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now our young girls\Nhave taken to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have seen flowers blooming\Nthat had never bloomed before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and we are now reaping the\Nharvest of our barren crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now today, we shall\Nsend off two more girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:22.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am certain that they, too,\Nshall bring us great fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:51.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their Portraits
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:04.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get a move on! Let's not keep\Nthe client waiting forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it, Wauf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if\Nyou're a man or a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or even a former sibylla,\Nfor that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:20.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,You work for me now! And I'm\Nnot cutting you any slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, right, so what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:25.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to pick up the pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You need to go easy on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is it, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is it, sweetheart?\NMommy said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to ask you what you wanted for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:39.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, everything your\Nmommy makes is so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,She said you're not\Nallowed to say "anything"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,She did? All right, that's\Ngoing to be a tough one then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:52.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,So listen, this is the\Nmost critical time for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want Waporif coming\Nafter me if you overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:05:00.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've heard that if you just keep moving,\Nyou can pop out the baby, 1-2-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:04.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,But thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what are we having for lunch, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm, let's see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:18.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, didn't you\Njust finish your night shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,The highlands and Shoukoku\Nare already waging a cold war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:28.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,They could void the peace treaty any\Nday, and then they'll drag us into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,War again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eliph! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:34.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,They saved us back there, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:06.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've stolen a Simoun and\Nallowed the sibyllae to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you realize the magnitude\Nof what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:36.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they should revolt\Nagainst our country...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:42.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong idea.\NAll they're going to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is carry themselves away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the Land of Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a guest to tend to now, so\Nit'll have to be a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, try to get along now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:12.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, try to get along now!\NYes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such lively children!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know. It's all I can\Ndo to keep up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:27.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I tried to negotiate with them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there's not much more I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:33.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this place wouldn't even\Nexist without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:34.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I'm so grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, there has to be\Nanother way. I'll find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once war is officially declared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:44.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there will be more and more\Nvictims like these children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're not really victims though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. They've lost a\Nlot because of the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:55.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but they still have\Nso much to live for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're our seeds of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:02.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their footsteps will one day\Nring out across the Land of Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of Hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,"The Land of Hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,For someone who was once\Na priestess long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...those words have\Nsuch a nostalgic ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought it was only a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:30.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,But even if the legend is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:36.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what purpose could there be in\Nperforming the Emerald Ri Majon now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:40.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no longer any\Nvalue to the word "purpose."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, if we looked hard enough,\Nwe might find such a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,But even if we'd found one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the girls would never\Nhave chosen it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:00.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:06.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take our Simouns and pursue\Nthe Sibylla Aurea's Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:10.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you insane? Do you\Nintend to shoot them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:40.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our hands are tied. There's\Nnothing we can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to go back to our jobs now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:53.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,It will be all right, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if they go after them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if they go after them now...\NBut, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Aer and\NNeviril will make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, your nose is running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, since when are\Nyou such a crybaby, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:22.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, come on. I'm\Nsure Aer and Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, you're breathing on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, you're breathing on me...\NWhat? Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm gonna get\Nall touchy-feely too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then let's do that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:33.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!\NMe too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:33.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on! Stop it, Alty!\NMe, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on! Stop it, Alty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister! Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dad's clothes! Alty! Get that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:12.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother. All that time\Nwe spent doing laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:15.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,This weather's so weird. Guess we'll\Njust have to wash everything again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, all you do is sit\Nthere and watch, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, that's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you. My fever has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I finally understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what you meant after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're all going to fly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Into a sky where nothing\Nis ever certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Towards a hope that they\Ncan't even be sure exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I made everyone learn how\Nto do the Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...yet I don't even\Ntake to the skies myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you want to fly again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:52.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if you don't want\Nto do it, Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll never fly with anyone as my pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but you, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:15.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:28.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry! They're\Ngoing to catch up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:32.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're going to do a Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry up then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never seen that Ri Majon before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Morning Calm Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morning Calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:54.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I read about that one\Nonce in an old book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's performed to bid farewell to\Ncomrades about to depart on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,To bid farewell to comrades\Ndeparting on a journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:12.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Morning Calm Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:21.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:26.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,There was also a time in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Long ago, we were all maidens too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:55.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go now, Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:12.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,To a place where you and I can be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:16.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's go, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for bringing\Nyou here, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's all right. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,You see, I want you to pair up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I already told you no once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll only...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:46.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,But does Dominüra ever intend\Nto fly again? I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, wasn't that a Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ultimate form of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:25.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:26.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ultimate love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which sky shall we journey towards next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! You got here early, Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, wait. I mean Vuraf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's awkward for you\Nto call me that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:16.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Vura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Vura. Why\Ndon't you come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:20.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you get one too, Vura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:28.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war hasn't even started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess former sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...have the honor of being the first\Nto be shipped out at times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which side?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,My hometown is on the\Nother side of the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:43.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be fighting for Shoukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're going to be enemies then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:52.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Here, have some of our\Nlocal vegetables! New strain, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I need to make a killing on these...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and find myself a lovely bride.\NI can't die till I've done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Becoming a man hasn't\Nchanged you at all, Floef!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say, isn't it?\NYou can just call me Floe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that the Arcus Prima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:21.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I thought I might as well\Nlive where I can always see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I picked this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,A sunken luxury liner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose there's an allure to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, that might be bad luck to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see\Nyou on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:39.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right then. How's goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:43.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:10.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder why none of us could let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:14.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The idea of sending Aer and\NNeviril off to that other world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:20.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was it because we wanted to defy\Nthe inescapable flow of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were afraid to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to stay the way\Nwe were as young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did we project those feelings\Non to Aer and Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:35.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we wanted to do\Nwas to leave our mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:39.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,To prove that we once\Nexisted, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to shout that\Nout to the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:47.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The fact that we were\Nonce really here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to leave our mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to raise our voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:05.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:17.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where are you, our eternal maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such a nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,It certainly is a nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:48.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:52.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:59.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:07.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:19.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:25.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:29.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:33.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.19,0:23:38.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:44.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:47.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:53.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:59.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
